{"tid":1200863,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"今晚食宵夜既朋友","createTime":"2019-06-11T00:27:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-11T01:16:14.000Z","uid":37516,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"2b864bfda3c18cdbefb910ab3ac8f63b15aec182","tid":1200863,"uid":37516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T00:27:31.000Z","msg":"如果到時真係人少的話請堅持到12日朝早<br />\n港豬係日頭先出現<br />\n大家唔好比人拉/受傷<br />\n雖然咁講好冇志氣<br />\n但係大堆港豬出現之前我地要保持人數<br />\n所有衝擊主力就係呢段時間呢一班人<br />\n少一個就少一個<br />\n<br />\n最後，點係條街捱成晚？<br />\n銅鑼灣有k唱有夜開鋪頭<br />\n或者比狗追散左<br />\n記住去人多燈多既地方<br />\n千其唔好諗住自己一個跑去冇人地方冇人搵到你<br />\n<br />\n天佑香港<br />\n天佑義士"},{"pid":"8a63662613be3e3efb6a99ddf549d246273cb872","tid":1200863,"uid":37516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T00:27:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f768c25d32da0c1fe82da0b9ff1a7b0f459b61c","tid":1200863,"uid":37516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T00:29:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3200db9a7b3bf630590c9952b8aebfcb61ac665e","tid":1200863,"uid":37516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T00:31:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26b926261a8e378ad4d362fb3628c9babedaf019","tid":1200863,"uid":94075,"like":0,"dislike